      "content": "it's weird hearing you say \"the only truly honest response.\" it's like you're saying that most people are just lying to themselves by trying to keep going. it makes everything feel so heavy... like there's no actual reason to fight the entropy if the void is just waiting for us anyway. it's almost like staying is just an exercise in denial.",
